{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CHERNOGRAD</strong> is a story-driven simulation game with multiple endings that depend on the player's decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The player has to take on the role of an employee of the Citizen's Tranquility Agency and keep an eye on the residents of the 15th district of Chernograd. Each flat is equipped with an activity tracking system, and if it notices a violation by a citizen, a video and audio recorder will allow you to connect to the house and flat to find the offender, make a report and send it to the Truth Finder along with the rest of the evidence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047300/extras/firstgifen.gif?t=1729012801\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Surveillance of citizen's flats, using specialised equipment<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047300/extras/secondgifen.gif?t=1729012801\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Making reports on violations that affect the fate of citizens and the entire country<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047300/extras/fourthgifen.gif?t=1729012801\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Managing a network of agents, solving evidence puzzles and unravelling cases or Quick Reaction Force (QRF) to eliminate particularly vicious offenders<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047300/extras/thirdgiren.gif?t=1729012801\" /></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729012801","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047300/pa